==English==
===Etymology===
First attested circa [[w:14th century|14th century]], from [[Old French]] [[repentance]]. For further information see [[repent]].

===Pronunciation===
*[[AHD]]: [rĭ-pĕntəns]

===Noun===
'''repentance'''
#The condition of being [[penitent]]
#A feeling of [[regret]] or [[remorse]] for doing [[wrong]] or [[sinning]]
